                                                              <br/> 
                                <div class="phototagleft">
                                  Photo: Shane Epping
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p><a href="https://keijaparssinen.com/"><strong>Keija Parssinen</strong></a> is the author of the novels <em>The Ruins of Us</em>, which received the Michener-Copernicus Award, and <em>The Unraveling of Mercy Louis</em>, which earned an Alex Award from the American Library Association. She is currently an associate professor of English and creative writing at Kenyon College.</p>
                                            <div class="clear"></div>
                                                          
